                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-378-18740504 t18740504-378-punishment-43"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Robert Malcolm Kerr, Esg;.</hi>
